# Cloudflare Pages static guard for Phase 0.
#
# The deployed Pages site is static-only. Until the real Read Worker is
# deployed, every /v1/* request must resolve to an explicit JSON sentinel
# instead of falling through to index.html and looking like an API drift.
#
# Cloudflare Pages applies the 200 rewrite before SPA fallback.
/v1/* /v1-api-unavailable.json 200
